text: Kazi Rabbi Hasan is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Joypurhat-2. ==Career== Hasan was elected to parliament from Joypurhat-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Kazi Rabbi Hasan
